# Frontend (Vite + React)

- Modules: `src/modules/<domain>/` — no cross-module imports; export via `index.ts`.
- TypeScript strict; no `any` in new code. No `console.log` in production paths.
- Styling: CSS Modules only (`.module.css` / `.module.scss`). No Tailwind in JSX, no inline `style={{}}`, no hardcoded colors outside `src/styles/globals.css`.
- API calls in services or `src/lib/api.ts` — not in page components.
- Shared UI only in `src/components/`. Use semantic HTML and `aria-label` on icon buttons.
- Supabase URL/key: `src/utils/supabase/info.tsx` — `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` required in `.env.local`.
